    "markdown_formatted": "## Meeting Purpose\n\n[Verify the AWS account for the Rhetoric dev environment.](https://fathom.video/share/[REDACTED:TOKEN]?tab=summary&timestamp=169.0)\n\n## Key Takeaways\n\n  - [**AWS Verification Blocked:** The verification process for the `dev@rethoric.com` account is blocked, as it requires a credit card to complete registration.](https://fathom.video/share/[REDACTED:TOKEN]?tab=summary&timestamp=450.0)\n  - [**MFA Decision:** Multi-Factor Authentication (MFA) was skipped to avoid tying the shared account to a single user's device, ensuring team access.](https://fathom.video/share/[REDACTED:TOKEN]?tab=summary&timestamp=377.0)\n  - [**Development Update:** Marco is focused on resolving voice-related issues to deliver current features by Friday.](https://fathom.video/share/[REDACTED:TOKEN]?tab=summary&timestamp=603.0)\n  - [**AI Automation Brainstorm:** The team discussed using new AI tools (Perplexity, Cloud Code) to automate workflows like financial analysis and lead generation.](https://fathom.video/share/[REDACTED:TOKEN]?tab=summary&timestamp=32.0)\n\n## Topics\n\n### AWS Account Verification\n\n  - [The team followed Marco's guide to verify the `dev@rethoric.com` account, which is the root user for the Rhetoric AWS environment.](https://fathom.video/share/[REDACTED:TOKEN]?tab=summary&timestamp=260.0)\n  - [**Process Steps:**](https://fathom.video/share/[REDACTED:TOKEN]?tab=summary&timestamp=260.0)\n    1.  [Log into the `dev@rethoric.com` Gmail account.](https://fathom.video/share/[REDACTED:TOKEN]?tab=summary&timestamp=260.0)\n    2.  [Access the AWS console via the root user login.](https://fathom.video/share/[REDACTED:TOKEN]?tab=summary&timestamp=327.0)\n    3.  [Search for and select Amazon Simple Email Service (SES).](https://fathom.video/share/[REDACTED:TOKEN]?tab=summary&timestamp=310.0)\n  - [**Blocker:** The process is blocked at the \"Complete Your AWS Registration\" step, which requires a credit card.](https://fathom.video/share/[REDACTED:TOKEN]?tab=summary&timestamp=450.0)\n      - [**Rationale:** This is a standard AWS security measure to confirm identity and prevent abuse.](https://fathom.video/share/[REDACTED:TOKEN]?tab=summary&timestamp=450.0)\n      - [**Action:** Eduardo will provide the card details to proceed.](https://fathom.video/share/[REDACTED:TOKEN]?tab=summary&timestamp=450.0)\n\n### Development Status\n\n  - [Marco reported that current development is focused on resolving voice-related issues.](https://fathom.video/share/[REDACTED:TOKEN]?tab=summary&timestamp=603.0)\n  - [**Goal:** Deliver all current features with correct functionality by Friday.](https://fathom.video/share/[REDACTED:TOKEN]?tab=summary&timestamp=630.0)\n\n### AI Automation Brainstorm\n\n  - [Carlos shared ideas for using new AI tools to automate business workflows.](https://fathom.video/share/[REDACTED:TOKEN]?tab=summary&timestamp=32.0)\n  - [**Perplexity (Pro/Max Tiers):**](https://fathom.video/share/[REDACTED:TOKEN]?tab=summary&timestamp=43.0)\n      - [**Capability:** Schedule tasks with computer access (e.g., browse the web, analyze data).](https://fathom.video/share/[REDACTED:TOKEN]?tab=summary&timestamp=43.0)\n      - [**Use Cases:**](https://fathom.video/share/[REDACTED:TOKEN]?tab=summary&timestamp=63.0)\n          - [Automated financial analysis of stocks (e.g., NVIDIA).](https://fathom.video/share/[REDACTED:TOKEN]?tab=summary&timestamp=43.0)\n          - [Weekly summaries of companies that raised capital → for sales outreach.](https://fathom.video/share/[REDACTED:TOKEN]?tab=summary&timestamp=83.0)\n  - [**Cloud Code:**](https://fathom.video/share/[REDACTED:TOKEN]?tab=summary&timestamp=100.0)\n      - [**Capability:** Remote monitoring and control from a phone.](https://fathom.video/share/[REDACTED:TOKEN]?tab=summary&timestamp=100.0)\n      - [**Status:** Carlos's account is currently blocked (\"Remote Control is not enabled\").](https://fathom.video/share/[REDACTED:TOKEN]?tab=summary&timestamp=100.0)\n\n## Next Steps\n\n  - [**Eduardo:** Provide credit card details to complete AWS registration.](https://fathom.video/share/[REDACTED:TOKEN]?tab=summary&timestamp=450.0)\n  - [**Marco:** Resolve voice-related issues to deliver current features by Friday.](https://fathom.video/share/[REDACTED:TOKEN]?tab=summary&timestamp=603.0)\n  - [**Marco:** Schedule a follow-up meeting for Friday to review the delivery.](https://fathom.video/share/[REDACTED:TOKEN]?tab=summary&timestamp=630.0)\n",
